settings.description: When were there so many pipes in the sky? Who knows, but for whatever reason Mario needs to get through all the piranhas and koopas.

A flood has happened in Pipe Maze! There is no explanation but you must get through the maze. It's easy to escape.
 Based on this video: https://youtu.be/BWXblAObfrg

Just keep running, and don't stop! Let the triangular blocks guide you!
Difficulty: 2/5
A long and vegetable filled adventure. A mini Mario game I guess?
Giant enemies among this plains stage.
A nasty short showcasing the unpredictability of chain chomps.  see if you make make it through!
A partial recreation of 8-4 from Super Mario Bros.
